column6: The stage is set for the biggest SUPERIOR SPIDER-MAN story of them all! And it starts here with a goblin fight like no other: The Green Goblin vs. The Original Hobgoblin! Plus: That thing that happened at the end of #25... That thing that raised all of those questions... You don't have to wait any longer. You'll get your answers THIS ISSUE! Honest.
column8: | artist:Pasqual Ferry | writer:Dan Slott | penciller (cover):Ryan Stegman
